Package: LuminaTable
Title: Beautiful Interactive Tables for R and Shiny
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: person("Dimitri", "Tselenchuk", email = "dtselenc@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create beautiful, interactive tables with custom themes, search, sorting, and pagination. Features a lightweight custom rendering engine (LuminaEngine) with Excel-inspired styling and support for sparklines, row selection, and column filters.
